premise_source_doc_sentence: Dennis Edwards  (  born February 3 , 1943  )  is an American soul and R&B singer , notably a lead singer in The Temptations , on Motown Records .
Edwards joined the Temptations in 1968 , replacing David Ruffin and sang with the group from 1968 to 1976 , 1980 to 1984 and 1987 to 1989 .
